Press release: evolution simulation game 'The Sapling'

**Message**
Dear writers and editors of [x],

Today I want to announce my game The Sapling. It is a short simulation game where you design your own plants and animals, and put them in a world together. Or you turn on random mutations, and see what evolution does to your ecosystem!

[image a] [image b]

All code, graphics and music is created by me. I explain how everything works in this 'first look' video:

[Youtube link]

The game will be released December 12, and I will gradually release more details over the coming weeks. For more information, see [the website] and [the presskit]. If you have more questions, you can reach me via this email address. Today I will also be available all day (CEST) on Skype, my username is stoopwessel .

Best regards,
Wessel Stoop



